data.description:
Welcome home to 9366 Newton Falls Rd. This sprawling Ranch was built in 2008 and has a wonderful open floor plan and sits on 5.15 acres of land! Truly one floor living in this 4 bedroom 2 full bath home. Master bedroom with walk in closet, and its own full bathroom. the other 3 bedrooms are very generous in size and closet space. The foyer is open and bright, and takes you into the oversized living room with vaulted ceilings connected to the kitchen and dining room area. The kitchen has plenty of cabinet space, an island and all appliances that were installed in 2021. There is a lovely sun/morning room that walks out to the brand new deck completed in 2023. All new lighting throughout the the home was installed in 2022, the furnace and A/C, replaced in 2021, as well as hot water tank 2021, a new well was drilled in 2021. 2023 2 additional bedrooms were added.
There is a 56x32 detached garage/pole barn with new concrete floors in outbuilding 2021, added 200amp panel, new sliding and insulation, and wired for 220 outlets. Water line is ran from the house to the outbuilding, and you also get an attached 2 car garage!
